title: Bit Banger
info:
1st place at Oldschool 4K compo at Revision 2011


from readme:
-----------------------------
A digital and analogue experiment built
around an ATtiny15: 1.6 MHz, 1 kB ROM,
32 bytes (!) RAM.

VGA and mono sound generated with software
and a few analogue components.
